<section class="section" aria-labelledby="about-h">
<div class="inner">
  <div class="sec-head">
    <span class="tag tag-dim" style="margin-bottom:16px;display:inline-flex;">About this stack</span>
    <h2 id="about-h">The Complete Free Shopify Automation Stack in 2026</h2>
    <p>Everything in one place — why it works, what it replaces, and why it costs $0.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="seo-prose" itemscope itemtype="https://schema.org/Article">
    <meta itemprop="headline" content="Free Shopify Automation Stack 2026 — Six Tools Replacing Paid Apps at $0">
    <meta itemprop="datePublished" content="2026-04-13">
    <meta itemprop="dateModified" content="2026-04-13">
    <meta itemprop="author" content="Stack Architect">
    <h3>What Is the $0 Shopify Automation Stack?</h3>
    <p>The $0 Automation Stack is a collection of six free tools that collectively replace the paid Shopify apps most stores spend $500–$900 per month on. Each tool uses a combination of <a href="https://www.make.com/en/register?pc=techie123" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Make.com</a>'s free automation tier, Google Sheets, and <a href="/go/systeme" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">Systeme.io</a>'s free plan to achieve the same technical outcome as paid alternatives — without any monthly subscription, developer cost, or code. Store owners who want the pre-built version can purchase the <a href="/pro">Complete Kit for $29</a> — four ready-to-import Make.com JSON blueprints that deploy in 10 minutes instead of 8 hours.</p>
    <h3>Why Replace Shopify Paid Apps With Free Automation?</h3>
    <p>The core problem most Shopify stores face is that the app ecosystem is structured around recurring revenue. Tracking apps charge $149–$299/month for server-side conversion data. Inventory apps charge $29–$199/month for real-time stock syncing. Email platforms like Klaviyo charge $150–$400/month for email automations that most stores never use at full capability. <strong>The $0 stack achieves the same technical outcomes — server-side tracking, live inventory, email automation, TikTok Events API, and real-time P&amp;L — using free tiers of tools built for automation at scale.</strong></p>
    <h3>Free Shopify Tracking — How CAPI Shield Replaces Elevar and Triple Whale</h3>
    <p><a href="/capi-shield">CAPI Shield</a> uses Make.com to route Shopify order webhooks directly to Meta Conversions API and Google Enhanced Conversions server-to-server. iOS restrictions, ad blockers, and cookie expiry cannot intercept server-side signals. Stores typically recover 20–40% of conversion data that was previously invisible to their ad platforms — improving ROAS attribution without paying $149–$299/month for a third-party tracking tool. <a href="/elevar-alternative">Elevar charges $150+ per month</a> for the same server-side tracking infrastructure. CAPI Shield achieves identical EMQ scores (7–8.5) at $0. <a href="/triple-whale-alternative">Triple Whale charges $299+ per month</a> for attribution data that server-side tracking provides natively.</p>
    <h3>What Replaces Shopify Stocky After August 2026?</h3>
    <p>Shopify is permanently closing Stocky on August 31, 2026 and deleting all data after that date. <a href="/stocky-swap">Stocky Swap</a> is the best free Stocky replacement — it logs every Shopify order to Google Sheets in real time via a Make.com webhook, capturing stock levels, fulfilment status, and full order history. It deploys in 4 minutes, costs $0 forever, and requires no Shopify app install. For a full comparison of <a href="/stocky-alternative">all Stocky alternatives in 2026</a>, including paid options, see the dedicated comparison page.</p>
    <h3>Free TikTok Server-Side Tracking for Shopify</h3>
    <p>The same Make.com scenario can branch to <a href="/tiktok-events-api-shopify">TikTok's Events API</a> simultaneously. TikTok uses CompletePayment as its purchase event name. The server-side signal bypasses iOS ITP and ad blockers, achieving EMQ scores of 6–8 in most Shopify deployments — the same technical outcome as WeltPixel at $39/month or Analyzify at $99/month, at $0. For a full no-code walkthrough, see <a href="/how-do-i-set-up-tiktok-events-api-on-shopify-without-code">how to set up TikTok Events API on Shopify without code</a>.</p>
    <h3>Free Klaviyo Alternative — Systeme.io</h3>
    <p>Klaviyo changed its billing model in February 2025 — stores now pay for every active profile whether they email them or not. <a href="/replace-klaviyo-free">Systeme.io's free plan</a> includes 2,000 contacts with unlimited email sends, full automation sequences, sales funnels, CRM, and affiliate management. For stores not using Klaviyo's advanced ecommerce segmentation, the migration takes 30 minutes and saves $150–$400/month permanently. For a full breakdown of the difference, see the <a href="/klaviyo-vs-systeme-io">Klaviyo vs Systeme.io comparison</a>. Stores that need more advanced segmentation than Systeme.io can also consider <a href="https://try.getresponsetoday.com/gejtf3pvvf1u" target="_blank" rel="noopener sponsored">GetResponse</a> as a Klaviyo alternative.</p>
    <h3>Free Shopify P&amp;L Reporting — Live Google Sheets Dashboard</h3>
